title: Omni Porcelain Kettles
transcripts: Hi I'm Tracy with cuisinart here to talk to you about resorts newest line of teakettles. This is our Omni enamel tea kettle line. Depending upon the style of your kitchen it offers you a variety of colors to choose from. Comes in three colors white red and black. It is a natural over stainless steel and the great thing about stainless steel is that it heats very quickly and efficiently. And it also has to stay cool handle which offers protection. And each of the kettles also come with a whistle to signal that the water is at a boiling point and it's ready for your cup of tea coffee or meal. Whatever your desire and it's also backed by cuisinarts lifetime guarantee so savor the good life with its new Omni enamel tea kettle line.
